1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:03,392
Each Funder receives only its own RFQ package

2
00:00:03,392 --> 00:00:05,898
and submits its own Private Quote.

3
00:00:05,898 --> 00:00:10,134
A valid quote requires a committed demo allocation

4
00:00:10,134 --> 00:00:12,252
compatible with CIP fifty-six.

5
00:00:12,252 --> 00:00:16,947
That allocation must match the RFQ, Seller, amount,

6
00:00:16,947 --> 00:00:19,882
token administrator, and validity window.

7
00:00:19,882 --> 00:00:24,106
Competing Funders cannot inspect one another's requests, prices,

8
00:00:24,106 --> 00:00:25,690
or commercial terms.
